      "date": "2013-12-08 06:57:38.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/034a6c9e-5fd6-11e3-a960-52540035b04c).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
